a:r.a:t: Capital Expenditures and Free Cash Flow
Katuns capital expenditure requirements are less than 0.5% of revenue
Maintenance expenditures are expected to remain constant at 0.2% of revenue
Maintenance expenditures include computer hardware and software and general facility upkeep
Growth expenditures are projected as a percentage of year over year revenue gains with a nominal increase of 20 bps from 0.1% in 2017F to 0.3% in 2021F to support the 3.0% CAGR from 2017F to 2021F
Growth expenditures are largely for laboratory equipment
Unique business model with consistently low capex leads to attractive cash conversion
